Subject: Re: [T2] Generator Removal Uhhh!

The thermostat shouldn't affect things.  Reach around the front of the
shroud and make sure that the fan is loose on the hub, and make sure that
the washers and shims are removed from the front of the fan.  If the fan
is frozen to the hub it will make things hard to remove.

George Lyle

